            <abstract id="ref39" label="Abstract">The Books and Arts Associate Records focus on the finances of Books and Arts Associates, a group within Time Inc. that monitored Time Inc.'s minority investments in foreign publishing houses. Included are newsletters, strategic plans, budget reports, operating reports, presentations, policies and procedures manuals, and correspondence.</abstract>
